title: SMTNY Classics: Middle Child Syndrome
itunes:title: SMTNY Classics: Middle Child Syndrome
description:
Do middle children really get the short end of the familial stick? Cristen and Caroline explore the psychological history of middle children, the influence of birth order and the cultural biases against the in-between siblings in this classic episode.
